            <lg xml:id="TK38">
<l>vīḻnāḷ paṭāamai naṉṟāṟṟi ṉaḵtoruvaṉ</l>
<l>vāḻnāḷ vaḻiyaṭaikkuṅ kal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If one does good and not a fallow day befalls, it shall become</l>
<l>a boulder in the way of coming lives.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
